column5: Hi, not sure what the rules dictate. Saw what looks like a sweet deal on a musky set up for someone posted on another fish board, can I post a link to it here? Or in the classifieds here?  It would be nice to see someone on this board get what appears to be a good deal, I don't know the seller or anything.
Thanks Roy, I'll post link in classifieds. And now I can sleep.
